   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I wouldn't be against such a change, but it appears that accommodating for `.NOTPARALLEL` would require significant changes to our build system. This is also a part of our codebase that attracts few contributors; as such, I'm not sure that this 30% improvement is worth the current burden and maintenance. ",
